parameters.name: YEAR
parameters.description: Year in which a new antenna configuration was selected.

parameters.name: DOY
parameters.description: ERT/UTC day of year on which a new antenna configuration was selected.

parameters.name: Hour
parameters.description: ERT/UTC hour at which a new antenna configuration was selected.

parameters.name: Minute
parameters.description: ERT/UTC minute at which a new antenna configuration was selected.

parameters.name: Second
parameters.description: ERT/UTC second at which a new antenna configuration was selected.

parameters.name: MET
parameters.description:
Mission elapsed time (MET) on the spacecraft clock
                                     when the new antenna configuration was selected.

parameters.name: Downlink Antenna
parameters.description:
Code for downlink antenna selected.  Possible values are:
                                          0: Front Fan beam
                                          1: AFT LGA
                                          2: Front LGA
                                          3: Back Fan beam
                                          4: FWD LGA5: Back LGA
                                          6: Front Phased Array
                                          7: Back Phased Array
                                          8: Hardware Error

parameters.name: Uplink Antenna
parameters.description:
Code for uplink antenna selected.  Possible values are:
                                          0: Front Fan beam
                                          1: AFT LGA
                                          2: Front LGA
                                          3: Back Fan beam
                                          4: FWD LGA
                                          5: Back LGA
                                          6: N/A
                                          7: N/A
                                          8: Hardware Error
